    {\displaystyle t_{1},\ldots ,t_{k}.}
   Thus the parameters 
  
    
      
        
          t
          
            1
          
        
        ,
        …
        ,
        
          t
          
            k
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle t_{1},\ldots ,t_{k}}
   and the coordinates 
  
    
      
        
