            1
          
        
        ,
        …
        ,
        
          x
          
            n
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{1},\ldots ,x_{n}}
   of the points of the variety are zeros of the ideal

  
    
      
        I
        =
        
          ⟨
          
            
              p
              
                0
              
            
            
              x
              
                1
              
            
            −
            
              p
              
                1
              
            
            ,
            …
            ,
            
              p
              
